Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:07.08,italics,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:15.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:33.48,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,While the members of the \NGolden Dawn were stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.48,0:00:36.50,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the Diamond troops from invading Kiten,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:43.33,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yami asked Vangeance something that had \Nbeen bothering him for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Vangeance...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:48.96,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Could you take off that mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.07,0:00:57.22,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yami, you suspect that I may be the leader of\Nthe Eye of the Midnight Sun, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.97,0:01:00.22,main,William,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.99,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:26.33,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,As Asta and Yuno were reunited during \Nthis battle and renewed their ambitions...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:29.33,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We're both working to \Nbecome the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.18,0:01:35.75,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...a new threat from the Diamond Kingdom \Nwas planning its next move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:52.86,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1023,1)}Never Again
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.71,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a lively bunch has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:30.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just not satisfied unless \Nyou're fighting something? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.27,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My head! It's going to crack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.31,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to break!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.50,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:35.08,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My body is moving on its own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:39.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever. You fought \Ndespite how broken you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:39.13,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami, I can't! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.75,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Spare me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:42.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Have him take a look at you and your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:44.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I think my head's being affected \Nmore now than it usually is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:47.97,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yami. Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:50.22,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:52.93,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This guy, who looks completely \Nout of place in this tower,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:57.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,is the kingdom's best quack doctor.\NYou might've gathered that from how he looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.16,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,That's so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:04:01.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,He managed to reattach one of my \Narms after it almost fell off before,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.51,0:04:03.64,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,so he's a great recovery mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.61,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Have him check you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:09.12,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get even more injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:11.71,top,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:16.62,sign_11079_109_Golden_Dawn_Vice,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(965,1)}Recovery Mage Who Works Directly Under the Wizard King\N{\fs30}Owen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:15.50,top,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Owen, a recovery mage who \Nworks directly under the Wizard King.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:16.62,top,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:19.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Asta! Thanks for seeing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.38,0:04:23.81,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,I hear all about you when \NI go out drinking with Yami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:25.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.25,0:04:29.18,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I heard that you can nullify magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:31.89,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew such magic existed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:35.65,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He works directly under the Wizard King?\NEven I know what that means!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:38.40,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,He must be an incredible quack doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:42.15,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Welp, I've got something \NI gotta take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.70,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a good feeling that\N I'm gonna win today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.41,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,You're going gambling, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:49.34,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,May Lady Luck be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:55.36,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... Yami's younger than me, \Nbut he's much bolder. It's so irritating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:57.76,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a bad guy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:58.61,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.45,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.45,0:05:01.67,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:04.42,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:15.02,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Water Recovery Magic: Qualle Operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:18.50,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they got you good, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:23.79,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you worry. My spell sees through \Nthe body of the person it envelops,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.79,0:05:26.86,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,so I can get a clear look at the affected \Narea and heal it with precision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:32.47,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Yami's amazing, but you've got \Nsome amazing muscles yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:34.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.75,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Now for some mana to promote healing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:44.71,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I finally got out of Kiten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:47.97,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Just how many captives \Ndid the Golden Dawn take?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.97,0:05:49.93,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, where's Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.85,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:54.76,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Jellyfish... recovery magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:03.06,main,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, Finral. Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:33.35,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, Asta. No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:35.50,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yami should show up any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.19,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:41.03,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami, did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.80,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I was on fire today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.90,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the huge bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.35,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Forget it. Let's just go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up with the spatial magic, Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:52.74,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.07,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure some of you noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.17,0:07:11.30,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but we've earned so many stars lately \Nthat we're actually out of the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:15.68,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This is all thanks to you \Ndumbasses working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:20.03,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So eat all this meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:23.44,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Swoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.22,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Swooshy, whooshy, whooshy, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:27.06,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Meat! Here! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:30.21,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Everywhere! All of the meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.74,0:07:36.03,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:39.59,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Mister Yami's actually treating us!\N Today's a damn holiday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:41.91,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna eat a lifetime's worth of meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:46.63,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie, I'll only serve you the best meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:48.62,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:52.30,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I've cooked this meat to just above \N55 degrees Celsius, just high enough
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:55.46,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,to make sure you don't get food poisoning, \Nbut below 60 degrees Celsius,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.46,0:07:57.03,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,since that would make it tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:59.06,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best-cooked meat possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:01.06,sign_11579_99_This_is_his_own_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,This is his own personal opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:03.15,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "Aah."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.07,main,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:16.49,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Magna, wanna kill each other \Nover this hunk of meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:17.44,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:19.41,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:26.26,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything more blissful \Nthan this? I can barely stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:30.51,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot! But so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:36.18,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,P-Pwease dun mook at muh ben \NI'm meating! It's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.82,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/Subs,0000,0000,0000,,You only eat barbecue with\N those who are special to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:42.77,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and I are special friends\N who share the same meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:46.56,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta, you can't eat with \Nyour arms like that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.56,0:08:50.23,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're so helpless. I'll just \Nhave to feed you myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:54.35,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo! I can eat with my feet now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:55.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess people can learn to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.16,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You filthy peasant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:03.62,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Finral! Show us a trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:06.00,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? O-Oh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:08.43,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Technique: Stop Hitting Yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:12.50,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right! You're next, Charmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:15.21,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Technique: Instant Disappearing Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:17.84,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La, la, la...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:21.73,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All you did was eat it instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:24.71,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Grey! You're next!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.71,0:09:25.81,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:28.78,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:29.85,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.82,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,S-Secret Technique: M****** ****xe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:40.56,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You just turned into what \Nyou usually turn into!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.01,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, everyone's so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:44.47,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has their own special skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:46.72,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,I have something that\NI've been secretly practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:47.91,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I show you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:51.92,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Special Technique: Crackling Magna Typhoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:55.09,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Technique: Meaty Sheepy Peacock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Next, I'll work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:00.63,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a special trick at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:07.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm exhausted. \NI'm gonna call it a night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.98,0:10:11.52,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all right. Make sure \Nyou get plenty of rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:14.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Great work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.65,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Asta acting a bit weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:25.83,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I mean, when does he ever get tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:30.83,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly. He just seems off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:36.42,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll go cheer him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:38.80,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if we try to kill \Neach other, he'll feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:42.09,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,He'll feel better if he eats \Nsome more meat, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:44.39,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:47.56,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,F-F-Forget I said anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:50.41,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it,\N the angle of his smile
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:52.12,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,seemed a little lower than usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:53.40,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.57,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, I have something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:02.70,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I overheard something when \NAsta was getting healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.39,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor said that Asta's arms
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:09.14,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,will never go back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:14.88,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:17.17,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What... are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:26.26,flashback,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like some kind of ancient \Ncurse has been placed upon them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:29.72,flashback,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, the bones are shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:34.42,flashback,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry, but I won't be able to \Nheal you with the magic I have now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:40.90,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,A curse, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:45.70,flashback,Vetto,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive... You managed \Nto draw me out, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:49.82,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what the best recovery \Nmage in the Clover Kingdom said,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:51.08,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,then there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:54.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:12:02.09,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I thought I'd \Nfound the ultimate partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:05.26,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,This is way too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.05,0:12:11.10,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The boy has no magic... and now \Nhe can't even use his only weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:14.64,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.64,0:12:16.31,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:18.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:32.79,flashbackitalics,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,You will never be able to \Nswing your sword again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:50.14,flashbackitalics,Owen,0000,0000,0000,,You will never be able to \Nswing your sword again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.65,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:05.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I'm gonna give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:09.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You just had to mess with \Nme again, didn't you, fate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:12.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But you're just firing me \Nup more, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:16.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna find a way to fix \Nthese arms, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:21.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll find some kind of strength \Nthat lets me fight without my arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:29.76,flashback,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,And you have no magic whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.64,flashback,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You must've been born that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:36.64,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then no matter how hard I try, \NI won't be able to use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:39.02,flashback,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:41.77,flashback,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You were born a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:46.19,flashbackitalics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to give...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That one time was the very last time
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.82,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ever going to feel depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:55.63,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:56.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:59.87,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Now that that's settled, time to train!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:59.13,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Damn straight, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:02.22,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,That's one hot-blooded guy, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:03.59,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:04.66,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:07.44,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna share my snacks with him later, la.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.44,0:14:10.45,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,H-His optimism is absolutely amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.27,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:16.08,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,His courage is admirable,\N but I won't let him near Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.93,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Admirable courage, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:20.43,top,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Yuno!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:22.07,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You can't give up, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:25.76,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Magic from that country \Nmight be able to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:37.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:39.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:43.44,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There's usually someone in \Nhere making things lively...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.88,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Did something about the base change again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.25,0:14:48.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Did everyone already head \Nout somewhere for the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:50.17,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:53.35,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone just slacking off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.35,0:14:55.54,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They were partying \Npretty hard yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:15:01.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I sense someone's ki.\NYou can't hide from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:05.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's Noelle and Finral.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:06.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What're they up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:10.57,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we were able to send \Nbasically everyone off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:13.17,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they'd all stop being so secretive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.62,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Asking me to send them places \Nbecause something came up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.62,0:15:18.81,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,or they suddenly remembered \Nthey had to be somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:22.66,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I know they're all sneaking away \Nto try and find a cure for Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:23.95,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.93,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Though I guess since they're not \Ntechnically going on missions,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:28.60,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Yami might get mad at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:30.68,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, Asta would \Nprobably say something like,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:34.51,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,"Forget about me! \NPlease put any missions first!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:52.49,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this place looks pretty rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:54.59,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You scared, Magna?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:57.57,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I am! I'm actually super excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:01.98,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Magna and Luck went to search some dungeon \Nin a barren part of the Forsaken Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:04.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:08.11,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche and Gordon are researching \Nhexes at the royal library.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:11.36,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hurry up and fix Asta's\Narms so I can hold his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:13.94,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,Our bond will get even stronger \Nif I can heal his wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.47,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be friends forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:15.84,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, BFFs...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:18.82,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Stop mumbling and search, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:23.74,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,"{\i1}100 Spells That'll Help You Become an Older \NBrother Your Little Sister Will Adore{\i0}."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:24.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.40,sign_23779_235_A_Beginner_s_Gui,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,A Beginner's Guide to Ancient Hexes That Even a Monkey Could Understand
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:32.73,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:36.20,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it might make Marie \Nsad if he doesn't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:39.80,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,Gauche is actually putting someone\Nelse before his sister for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:40.95,sign_12489_108_You_only_eat_bar,Gordon/subs,0000,0000,0000,,I need to work harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:49.69,top,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Charmy and Grey went to search for some \Nunknown ingredients that work against curses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:50.94,sign_24224_241_Grey,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(461,537)}Grey
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:51.41,top,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:55.17,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find you something that'll cure your \Ncurse, fill your tummy, {\i1}and{\i0} be yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:17:00.71,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,That's... I have no idea what \Nit is, but it smells delicious, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:03.47,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:04.93,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:06.27,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:09.86,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:13.25,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Cotton Creation Magic: Sheep Bondage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.99,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.99,0:17:20.94,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's keep moving forward, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:21.74,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:28.27,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought that the \Nmembers of the worst, lowest,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:31.49,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,and crudest squad would be \Nworking so hard for one newbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:34.23,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding. Especially for \Nsuch a dumb, reckless,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:37.09,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,vulgar, no-magic peasant like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:42.56,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to try so hard anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:45.52,flashback,Sekke,0000,0000,0000,,you filthy little rat that \Nwandered into the wrong place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:49.27,flashback,Koza,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that peasant \Nfrom the boonies saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.27,0:17:53.27,flashback,Revchi,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do a thing in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:57.41,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he doesn't have any magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:59.70,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,he just refuses to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.02,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he doesn't have any magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:06.75,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,he's the first one into the battle,\Nand he fights harder than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.00,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,And because he's like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.57,0:18:40.28,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta was able to give us \Nthe strength to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:44.29,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's our turn to help him fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:13.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I... wasn't blessed with any magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:16.75,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That always frustrated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:22.50,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But I sure was blessed \Nwith amazing friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:34.40,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Those dumbasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:38.09,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If only they'd work this hard \Nat their regular jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.98,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.98,0:19:43.84,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we also go look for somewhere \Npromising together— Crunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:47.68,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but there's somewhere \NI'd like you to take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:50.08,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You can go wherever you want on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.81,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:20:00.66,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I see! They might know \Nsomething that we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:02.03,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.53,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck did Vanessa go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.95,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,She disappeared before anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:13.07,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she has some kind of lead herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:16.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any time to waste, either.\N Hurry up and take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:21.62,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe remember you're asking your senior \Nfor a favor... But, yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:33.81,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.81,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:38.56,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.86,main,Fanzell,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey. I just got out of the bath—
